Author: Libertymind
Title: [ANN] MIROCANA.COM - FIRST ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE FOR TRANSPARENT INVESTING
Body: 1)  To get access to our investment products you should have at least 5000 MIRO for crypto-currency market, 10000 MIRO for currency and be in top200 token-holders to get access to the stock market product. But there is no minimum to invest, so join us here: https://app.mirocana.com  2) Now Oanda works in test mode, and there was an information about 2-3 days, for now less, to get access to trades for everyone, so you need to wait a little and we will announce when itâ€™s ok)  3) This is crypto-currency market, so not like forex, but it predicts 90 crypto-currency pairs that are available on Poloniex and Bittrex. We have also product for currency market. There our system can predict 125 currency pairs that are available with OANDA broker.  4) Mirocana analyzes activity of thousands of professional traders and is able to achieve a cumulative effect. Its final predictions are based on the opinion of many traders. Systems learn strong and weak sides of each trader to properly calculate the level of traderâ€™s importance in consensus prediction. And the activity of other traders is just one of many factors on which system base its predictions. we are unable to guarantee that we will have only profitable months, especially if you select high target return (with higher risks). We are focused on the accuracy of predictions and we are not in hurry, that is why for the first 8 months after a Token Sale we will not charge any commissions or fees for our service. We want to build a long-term and trustful relationships with our customers.  5) we operate globally. But some brokers or exchanges, that we have connection to, may have restrictions regarding opening an account for your country.

Author: cryptokrazy
Title: [ANN] MIROCANA.COM - FIRST ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE FOR TRANSPARENT INVESTING
Body: Please help me clarify the 5 issues below, so that I can understand everything better:  1) Initially, you had specified on the website that acquiring 5000 tokens during the ICO would allow you to use the product. Is that still the case?  2) Can the product be demoed right now on Oanda? If yes, how? The Medium link you provided earlier with more information has been suspended.  3) Also, I am trying to understand what your relationship with Mirocana and Oanda, IB and Poloniex is. Can you explain that? I have looked for press releases or articles from these three brokerage firms/exchanges mentioning Mirocana, but can't find anything.  4) I had read up on Mirocana back in September and thought that you had an interesting model. Back then, I think I read that access to Mirocana was going to be free for qualified token holders for 8 months and then you were going to take 25% of the profits generated by the users. If the user funds are going to be in their accounts at the respective brokers (Oanda, IB or Polo), what are the logistics for you to withdraw 25% of the gains from the accounts and will this be based on a high watermark? In addition to this, won't this make Mirocana similar to a hedge fund?  5) Finally, do US residents have access to Mirocana?  Thank you for clarifying these points. Everything sounds very interested and I may possibly want to invest.

Author: multibit
Title: [ANN] MIROCANA.COM - FIRST ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE FOR TRANSPARENT INVESTING
Body: The question is whether the leverage of your skills which you can achieve through AI does in the end bring about any individual advantages when everybody can use it. Imagine three people are in a competition for jumping as high as possible. Without a spring C was highest, B second and A the lowest jumper. Now they all get a spring as an extra tool. I suppose C will still be highest, B second and A last, at least as soon as enough practice was involved and C can use his superior power even with those springs. And I feel it will go the same way with someone having superior trading sense. If you give him the tools to leverage the skills he might remain the superior trader over others.

Author: Noruka
Title: [ANN] MIROCANA.COM - FIRST ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE FOR TRANSPARENT INVESTING
Body: The question is whether the leverage of your skills which you can achieve through AI does in the end bring about any individual advantages when everybody can use it. Imagine three people are in a competition for jumping as high as possible. Without a spring C was highest, B second and A the lowest jumper. Now they all get a spring as an extra tool. I suppose C will still be highest, B second and A last, at least as soon as enough practice was involved and C can use his superior power even with those springs. And I feel it will go the same way with someone having superior trading sense. If you give him the tools to leverage the skills he might remain the superior trader over others.

Body: I'm positive they weren't spamming, they were just asking the questions about the articles and asking the devs about the exact date of when the devs were going to release the official response. And now we are here again: they haven't answered half of the questions and promise to give us answers "somewhen soon". This does look sketchy as hell to me. All of those questions could be answered in 15 minutes.  Quote from: nobytes on October 25, 2017, 09:15:02 AM Quote from: wissy on October 25, 2017, 09:04:59 AM Quote from: the_donald on October 25, 2017, 05:32:27 AM Quote from: zgrdyg on October 25, 2017, 05:30:30 AM Quote from: Yasemin on October 25, 2017, 04:36:17 AM I checked out Mirocana telegram and for some reason, Ive got the feeling that there is a group of people attacking this project. There are so many post on this forum with critical questions and harming Mirocana's reputation. And I saw people firing questions in Telegram too.  I am highly suspicious that this is done deliberately to bring Mirocana down.  Why am I thinking this? Because there are so many scam ICO's going on right now and in the past, and I haven't seen that they have been accused for it. People just think, this is a scam and let it go. Why go through so much trouble?     Actually, it is a market that you can only trust yourself. Icos can be a scam, people spreading fud about ico can be paid or can be just invested competitor of the ico.  It is important to make your own inspection and made your decision based on it. It is the only way in this circumstances.  There are though groups of people trying to blackmail ICO's. they demand payment in bitcoin, else they're gonna spread the word that the project is a scam  Seriously?? People are capable of anything when money are involved. Hope, Mirocana's reputation won't be damaged because of these people. Well, as was already said, you really have to check all the information by yourself in order not to be led on.  He is telling the truth, this has happened before. Some devs have brought this these blackmail letters with screencaptures to our attention.  Please, ask Mirocana to provide such screenshots â€” they won't do that because they don't have any. I have never asked Mirocana for anything (especially, money) neither did I have ever blackmailed them. I started as a potential investor, checked their product, team, advisors and legal, gathered the questions in the article and asked them. Then I got banned for asking questions.  I did ask them to provide questions *fast* because their presale will end soon, and did claim that I will spread this article if they wouldn't answer the questions fast. So if you call the demands for answers to be blackmailing, let it be. I have never asked Mirocana for anything but the answers.

Title: [ANN] MIROCANA.COM - FIRST ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE FOR TRANSPARENT INVESTING
Body: Hello! We can connect our system to your account and start allocate your coins on your behalf. The rate of return that system will be able to generate directly depends on the accuracy of our predictions. You will be able to set up a target return in your Mirocana Account. This target annual return can be set from 5% to 200%. As the benchmark and a hedging asset we use Bitcoin itself. The rate of return will be calculated as the increase of your Bitcoin value of all of your assets to the increase of the Bitcoin. To put it simply, the rate of return is how strong you want outperform Bitcoin. We expect you not to take any actions on the account to which our system is connected. If you knowingly or accidentally open or close some trading orders, the system will not stop working. If you deposit more coins to the account or if you withdraw some coins from the account the system will notice that and it will automatically change the logic of money management and positions sizing. Author: Pajulapoiss
Title: [ANN] MIROCANA.COM - FIRST ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE FOR TRANSPARENT INVESTING
Body: Same article in Russian:   Quote from: Libertymind on October 21, 2017, 06:25:51 PM Quote from: zgrdyg on October 20, 2017, 08:58:39 AM Quote from: borodutch on October 20, 2017, 08:41:30 AM   Quote from: toolucky98 on October 20, 2017, 05:23:30 AM Quote from: borodutch on October 20, 2017, 05:10:32 AM Wrote an article with the thorough analysis of the Mirocana ICO: http://telegra.ph/CHestnyj-obzor-ICO-Mirocana-10-20.  I analyzed their team, advisors, product and legal aspect. Sorry, in Russian. Why didnt you write it in english ?   If so, maybe i will read it  Sorry... I wrote it for my audience at the Telegram channel which is primarily Russians. Quick summary would be: 1. Product is impossible to build with CEO's lack of the management experience, the only proof of concept they have doesn't work 2. Team lacks experience in their expertises 3. No relevant advisors on board, the case of adding 5+ fake advisors that never heard of Mirocana, only 4 advisors left on board out of ~15-20 4. Possible legal issues in Canada as their tokens can be considered as Securities if anybody asks OCS kindly to check Mirocana  That's pretty much it. I advised to invest in their ICO only to sell their coins at the peak. No possible long term profits as investors will start selling like crazy as soon as Mirocana launches.   Quote I contacted all 4 of them. They had around 15-20 advisor before the scandal with Mirocana using advisors' photos and names without their consent. After the cleanup they were left with 4 advisors and *none* of the advisors advise Mirocana on trading, investing or tech. One advisor is for legal issues, another advises how to make ICO, third one solely advises Mirocana on their finances (again, not on investing or trading but just accounting), fourth one haven't responded yet and will probably not respond (Peter).  I personally like this Project but still, this are important issues.  Mirocana dev is very active on thread, he will probably give detailed answers for this issues.     Hey, we will answer about this issue sooner or later, don't be worry!    Very reassuring, don't you think?

But this is trading software from a startup so it's okay to be a little paranoid. I'm rambling a bit but I'm sure all of you remember Volkswagen and other car manufacturers having the car software react differently in lab tests than on the road. Just saying, it's improbable but these things happen, you know.  Now I think about it, my previous question about Mirocana's guarantees and safeguards is nonsense. If you're going to use safeguards you should set them in your trading account, not in the system that sends the trading signals.

Title: [ANN] MIROCANA.COM - FIRST ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE FOR TRANSPARENT INVESTING
Body: Well the Mirocana system will probably work with API keys like most other trading platforms. In those API keys you can give permissions to what an external resource is allowed to do (selling, buying, transfering, etc..) Regarding the disastrous trade... It could always happen that the bot/software does something which is bad. I would start with creating a new account on my trading system and just use a small amount of trading money for a couple of weeks to see how the system performs. Never go all-in in the beginning.

Author: Libertymind
Title: [ANN] MIROCANA.COM - FIRST ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE FOR TRANSPARENT INVESTING
Body: Hi, Noruka! Mirocana has some really specific differences. The first difference from others is that we do not take customers funds to our accounts. We connect to your broker or exchange account using an access key and manage your funds there. The second difference is that we are building three platforms for crowd-sourced learning that will improve the overall accuracy of our predictions. And we will use our tokens to pay the rewards to skillful people for their help. The third difference is that we base our predictions on many data sources (some of them described here: mirocana.com/technology). Our predictions not only based on moving averages but on many factors, like technical indicators, correlations, chart patterns, other players' activity, news, articles, tweets and even Google Trends. The fourth difference is that we work not only with crypto-currencies but with traditional markets as well, check our products: mirocana.com/products

Author: Libertymind
Title: [ANN] MIROCANA.COM - FIRST ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE FOR TRANSPARENT INVESTING
Body: Good day, poiseulle! Why it's not decent? The difference is huge. We write trading strategies (and soon anyone can write them for us for MIRO tokens) and use AI-tools like deep-leaning neural nets to combine all strategies together into one "super-strategy" that has a better investment performance than any other strategy individually. Then we wrap this strategy into investment products. And you can get access to these products if you have enough MIRO tokens.  Enigma didn't create their own syntax for writing new strategies. They used open-sourced Pipeline from Qunatopian. We have developed our own syntax and framework for writing and backtesting the strategies that is faster and much more scalable.

Author: tansoft64
Title: [ANN] MIROCANA.COM - FIRST ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE FOR TRANSPARENT INVESTING
Body: #mirocana  Complex AI trading algorithms for advanced capital gains   Trying to imagine the ideal trading advisor, you see someone with unlimited resources in hands, who avoids the human factor, catching up on activities of other traders, analysts and hedge-fund managers, following all the news, articles and other data. It doesnâ€™t seem to be a human being with all that capabilities. Modern deep learning neural nets give a possibility to have an unlimited access to systems like that, which are ready to give you the solution based on the factors taking place at this very moment on trading market and establish its predictions on the decisions of thousands of professionals.  Some will say that only limited number of market players can afford AI-powered trading robots. However, Mirocana project was developed to prove that everyone can use complex deep-learning technologies in order to increase the funds.  Mirocana is a multi-layered predicting system for stock, currency and crypto-currency markets that uses deep-learning neural nets to analyze all kinds of financial data. It does not take your funds to its accounts, withdraw or transfer them. You will be able to select target annual return that you want the system to achieve, and it will show associated risks. Absolutely free to use for 8 months straight, compensating 25% of the losses in the end this period.  Mirocana consists of three products for stock, currency and crypto-currency markets: As a Stock Market Solution, Mirocana system uses predictions for over 400 companies that are traded on NYSE and NASDAQ stock exchanges. As a Currency Market Solution, the system predicts 125 currency pairs that are available with OANDA broker. As a Crypto-Currency Solution, it predicts 90 crypto coins that are traded on the Poloniex exchange. You are able to set up a target annual return in your account, the higher you set it, the more risks system will take to achieve it.  The Mirocana engine was developed without any third parties involved, allowing the team to constantly expand the possibilities of the project. The deep-learning neural nets help the system to make predictions using all possible strategies at once, combined with any media mentions and trading news forecasts. Mirocana analyzes tons of cumulated information to give you the best decision that is available at this moment.The system also learns strong and weak sides of human traders based on their experience and then turns it into new strategies. If a particular strategy is no longer performing wellâ€Šâ€”â€Šit will be given lower priority in the process of decision-making, so it will not affect the final result.  The team of the project consists of talented developers, data scientists and analysts, who are supported by experts from finance, legal and blockchain industries. The system also attracts a lot of people from all over the world, who is ready to contribute their knowledge and code to increase the accuracy of predictions. Their time and effort will be rewarded by MIRO tokens.  Mirocana is getting ready for a Token Sale to let the project reach as many people interested in trading as possible. Token Sale starts November 19. By buying MIRO tokens on the Token Sale, you are buying an access key to three Mirocana trading solutions. During the Pre-Sale stage, you can get a discount of 5 to 40% off your MIRO order, depending on the amount you are buying.

Title: [ANN] MIROCANA.COM - FIRST ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE FOR TRANSPARENT INVESTING
Body: Hey, lupanar! Great question!  Before Token Sale we will: 1) Create Token Sale investor cabinet on our website - Mirocana.com, where you will be able to:      1.1) Connect your OANDA account and see your balance and opened positions (without management)      1.2) Connect your Poloniex account and see your coins allocation (without management)      1.3) Purchase MIRO tokens during pre-sale (October 9 - October 19)      1.4) Purchase MIRO tokens during a Token Sale (November 19 - December 19)      1.5) See all past access session to your Mirocana account 2) Release Simulation results for our product for Currency Market (version 1.1) 3) Release Simulation results for our product for Crypto-Currency Market (version 1.1) 4) Release the first version of Mirocana Sigma platform and conduct first predicting tournament 5) Finish the creation of the Ethereum smart-contract and deploy it 6) Add new strategies and improve existing simulations for version 1.2

Author: ePesoInitiative
Title: [ANN] MIROCANA.COM - FIRST ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE FOR TRANSPARENT INVESTING
Body: The question is how intelligent is the Artificial Intelligence here. Is it discussed in the whitepaper? For me, it's just another iteration of a Poloniex trading bot.

Author: Libertymind
Title: [ANN] MIROCANA.COM - FIRST ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE FOR TRANSPARENT INVESTING
Body: Hey, ePesoInitiative! I understand that concern. We will publish the simulation results a bit later and it will be clear that our system is much more accurate than others. The main difference of our system is that it is modular and scalable.  Crypto trading bots that exist today are:    1) Based on one single strategy and implemented in a hard and static logic of if ... then ...    2) Based only on past prices history    3) Have a hard-coded logic of money management and position sizing  Mirocana system is:    1) Based on hundreds of strategies (and some strategies has hundreds of sub-strategies) and it uses deep-leaning neural nets to calculate the weights among all strategies in the system to achieve a cumulative effect and create a "super-strategy" that is better than any individual strategy by its own. It allows to create the system is not static and is able to adjust to changing market behavior.    2) Based not only quotes. We have strategies in the system that is based on the trading activity of other traders, based on news (they use sentiment analysis), based on macro data, based on correlations of assets. We will also analyze Bitcoin and Ethereum transactions and will try to create the strategy that will be based on that. In total, we have 40+ sources of financial data.    3) Each simulation has a logic of money management and position sizing that is not static. It takes into account a number of investment opportunities and previous investing performance.  To achieve that we have created:    1) Our own syntax and framework for writing new strategies and backtesting them.    2) A modular system of data collection that allows us to store and collect data from multiple data sources in real-time.    3) Our own framework for simulations that allow us to go through the history and understand how the system would behave. We run multiple experiments of weight distribution and see what is performing better. Then we deploy best performing simulation into production.    To make Mirocana system more accurate we will:    1) Release Mirocana Alpha platform where any interested algo-trader and quantitative analyst will be able to add his or her own strategy. If this strategy actually finds any patterns in data he or she will be rewarded with our tokens.    2) Release Mirocana Target platform where any person will be able to leave his or her future price forecasts and if these forecasts are accurate and consistent he or she will be paid with our tokens.    3) Release Mirocana Sigma platform where any data scientist or mathematician will be able to participate in our predicting tournament and try to create a predictive model of weights distribution among our strategies. If this model is better than ours, he or she will be paid with our tokens.  We successfully manage our own fund using the current version of the system and want to make it accessible to those who will support our research.

Author: Libertymind
Title: [ANN] MIROCANA.COM - FIRST ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE FOR TRANSPARENT INVESTING
Body: Hey, dsertov! We have developed our own syntax and framework for writing new strategies. It's similar to Qunatopian or OqantConncet frameworks. The difference is that our strategies produce predictions, but not investment decisions. And then we have a simulation that takes all predictions from all the strategies and calculates the weights among them using deep-learning neural nets and other ML-models. It allows us to create some sort of super-strategy that takes all the strategies in one.

Author: Libertymind
Title: [ANN] MIROCANA.COM - FIRST ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE FOR TRANSPARENT INVESTING
Body: Hey, EvRo74 and hoop! Sorry for a long reply! We have a lot of work to do.  Why the Poloniex? 1. Poloniex is the largest crypto-exchange out there. They have an API that restricts managing part and withdrawals. Moreover, they have margin trading. We will be adding new crypto-exchanges in the future (next one will be Bittrex) and customers who have access to our product for Crypto-Currency market will be able to choose the exchange they like.  Why the ETH? 2. We chose to base our tokens on Ethereum because it is the obvious choice. It is easy, many people have an experience purchasing ERC20 tokens and know how to do it. Moreover, it will be difficult to find smart-contract engineers if we would choose something else.  What is the maximum supply of tokens and is there any? 3. The supply of tokens is 200,000,000 MIRO, but only 65% of tokens will be for sale. You can find detailed token and processed distribution percentage on a token sale page: https://mirocana.com/token-sale The price of one MIRO token is 0,001 ETH. The contract of tokens is not deployed yet.  What will be the mechanism of mining work? 4. You, as a miner, install our app on the machine you want to mine on. This app asks our server for mining task. If there are any, app downloads the data it needs to run the task. There will be two types of tasks: backtesting strategies (in that case it downloads quotes + additional data) and backtesting simulation (it will download predictions from a large number of strategies and train neural nets on that data). The difficulty of the task is not known before it's done and can be only estimated. You will be able to see how much MIRO tokens you mined and with what speed in you Miner account on our website. According to our calculation will be much more profitable for miners than mining Ethereum or Bitcoin, especially for small miners.

Body: Hey, Calangaman! We will use the proceeds received from a token sale to increase the accuracy of the predictions (using our crowd-sourced learning platforms) that our system produces. It will eventually improve the quality of our investment products. More people would like to use our products, but since the supply of tokens (access keys) is limited, the price of the tokens will grow, which makes them even more interesting to purchase even for people that do not want to use our products. We will do very aggressive marketing campaign closer the Token Sale date.

Author: MindPower
Title: [ANN] MIROCANA.COM - FIRST ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE FOR TRANSPARENT INVESTING
Body: What a promising project, well done! I doubt there is anything similar to what you're doing, guys. I have a question - how exactly do you perform a simulation? How can people trust its outcomes?

Author: Libertymind
Title: [ANN] MIROCANA.COM - FIRST ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE FOR TRANSPARENT INVESTING
Body: Hey, MindPower! To my knowledge, there's no similar projects. Because, we have short track record, we will not charge any commissions for the first 8 months (average hedge-fund would charge you 20% of profits). Results of our simulations are as close as possible to the behavior of system on the past data. You can read more about the legitimacy of our backtesting on this page: https://mirocana.com/technology/

Author: Supercoiner111
Title: [ANN] MIROCANA.COM - FIRST ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE FOR TRANSPARENT INVESTING
Body: I have seen many netural net/AI trading/investing ICO what makes yours unique and outstanding?

Author: Libertymind
Title: [ANN] MIROCANA.COM - FIRST ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE FOR TRANSPARENT INVESTING
Body: Hey, Supercoiner111!  The first difference from Satoshi fund, the Token fund, and others is that we do not take customers funds to our accounts. We connect to your broker or exchange account using an access key and manage your funds there.  The second difference is that we are building three platforms for crowd-sourced learning that will improve the overall accuracy of our predictions. And we will use our tokens to pay the rewards to skillful people for their help.  The third difference is that we base our predictions on many data sources (some of them described here: mirocana.com/technology). Our predictions not only based on moving averages but on many factors, like technical indicators, correlations, chart patterns, other players' activity, news, articles, tweets and even Google Trends.  The fourth difference is that we work not only with crypto-currencies but with traditional markets as well, check our products: mirocana.com/products
